# ─── perception/ work dir: commit SOURCE (*.py) ONLY ──────────────────────
# Every data artifact under perception/ carries real clip-IDs and/or object names burned into
# filenames or pixels (grasp prompts, inventories, grounded review PNGs, depth frames). Source
# code is clip-agnostic; data is held-out. So: ignore everything under perception/ EXCEPT *.py.
perception/_*
perception/*.json
perception/*.png
perception/*.jpg
perception/*.jpeg
perception/*.npz
perception/*.npy
perception/*/
!perception/*.py
